*Consider External Vulnerabilities**:\\n   - Examine third-party software, systems, or internal networks for known vulnerabilities.\\n   - Use external assessments or reputable security tools to verify data security.\\n\\nBy combining these layers of security measures—ensuring encryption, proper key management, strong authentication, secure data storage, and robust network protection—you can significantly enhance the integrity and confidentiality of your received data. Always adhere to best practices and monitor for potential vulnerabilities in any area affected by external threats or internal issues.\"}]]},\"tokenUsageEstimate\":{\"completionTokens\":345,\"promptTokens\":14,\"totalTokens\":359}}}"}}
